---
title: Sweet & Spicy Chicken Lo Mein with Broccoli & Lime
description: This sweet and spicy noodle bowl features tender, chewy noodles tossed with juicy chicken breast and crisp-tender broccoli. It’s coated in an umami-rich sweet soy and chili glaze and finished with chili flakes, lime zest, and a bright squeeze of lime. In a quick 20 minutes you’ll be enjoying a better-than-take-out bowl of lo mein straight from your kitchen!
